  "displayName": "Monica Colangelo",
  "headline": "AWS Hero | Head of Hyperscaler Operations",
  "summary": "I am a technology leader, cloud expert, and AWS DevTools Hero with a strong technical foundation built over two decades in IT. Now Head of Hyperscaler Operations, I bring experience from a career path that started as a system administrator and progressed through DevOps engineering and cloud architecture. As a committed community builder, I lead several technical communities in Italy, organizing the AWS Community Day Italy and managing various AWS User Groups. I also founded The Cloud House, a non-profit organization dedicated to supporting and growing the tech community. As a passionate advocate for diversity in tech, I am dedicated to breaking barriers and creating pathways for women in technology. I speak at international conferences, sharing both technical insights and my experiences as a woman in tech leadership. Through mentoring, writing technical articles, and active community engagement, I work to inspire the next generation of women in technology and promote inclusive tech environments.",
